------------------------
go to browser
search - temp mail
https://temp-mail.org/en/
copy temp email address
ngrok - sign up
insert temp email addr
download ngrok
long press - copy link address
wget paste link  - .tgz extention file
ls
tar xvzf -file name  [for extraction]
ls    
---------------
revisit website
copy authentication token
./ paste and then enter
[your authentication token now will generated ]    
-----------------------------------------------
ngrok tcp 447      
[now running process - resolving tunnel ]  
it will connect soon 
press - ctrl+c for exit
---------------------------
[restart -ngrok]
ngrok http 8080 
[it will take time to connecting ]
then it will link
ngrok http 8080
------------------------
torn off wifi and use 
just try with mobile data  
